Explore Siyam World and its stunning facilities, plan your visit and activities from your device before and during your visit. Use this app to start planning your stay, and ensure you don’t miss-out on any of the incredible experiences on offer at Siyam World Maldives. During your stay the app provides the perfect travel companion, showing what’s on, providing you with fantastic inspiration from the recommended bucket list experiences which you can book directly from the app.  Your itinerary is always accessible to see what adventures you have planned.  
A personal concierge in your pocket!
About the Resort:
Siyam World is a striking new vision of the Maldives’ rich natural wonders, a carefree playground with an exciting, diverse, and endless array of ‘never-seen-before’ experiences to bask in a WOW! Premium All-Inclusive island getaway that crosses cultures and borders. Designed for fun-loving, open-minded couples, romance seekers, families or larger groups of friends, with the freedom to roam, socialise and engage in an island community. Siyam World is one of the largest islands in the Maldives to boast a resort and show-stopping residences - The Beach House Collection.


Use the app to help:
- Explore the services and facilities available at the resort;
- Perfect your stay by booking restaurant tables, excursions and activities such as snorkelling, scuba diving or spa treatments;
- view the entertainment schedule for the upcoming week;
- request to book any special events that you’d like to arrange for a loved one;
- book your next stay at the resort.
